> [truth](#comment_19_164W1rFVD9Bm7poGJWvjVUjvkbhhFC5nnt): How to Bypass ZeroTorrent or ZeroTalk quotas by creating new user accounts

Multiuser is different from new user account. You can edit user.json in your data folder and change the firsts lines:

"certs": {
      "zeroid.bit": {
        "auth_address": "1...", 
        "auth_privatekey": "5...", 
        "auth_type": "web", 
        "auth_user_name": "zeropunto", 
        "cert_sign": "..."
      }
    }, 

If you delete this lines ( "certs": {} ) you can create a new zeroid identity and switch from ones the the twos changing the "zeroid.bit": {}

